  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (180°C).",
    "Brown the beef in a large pan over medium-high heat. Remove from heat and set aside.",
    "In the same pan, sauté the onion and garlic until softened.",
    "Add the flour and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Gradually add the beef broth and milk, whisking continuously. Bring to a simmer.",
    "Return the beef to the pan and stir in the Worcestershire sauce.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a casserole dish.",
    "Top with shredded cheddar cheese.",
    "Bake for 25-30 minutes, or until the cheese is golden brown and bubbly.",
